window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>There are many things that go bump in the night, and I am one of them.</b></p> <p>As a vampyr who was born to fulfill a prophecy, my life was planned before I was created. I obeyed every rule, and I became the perfect vampyr, but one night changed everything.</p> <p>Rejected by the man who was destined for me, who was supposed to love me forever, I do the only thing I can. I flee into the night, nursing my broken heart.</p> <p>Being a rejected mate corrupts the soul, however, and in this game of Courts and Kings, nobody wins. Nobody except the monsters in the shadows. The monsters that save me, welcome me, and make me one of them.</p> <p>Welcome to the Court of Nightmares, where all your wicked dreams come true.</p>"; 
